{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "24", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "10", "M": "56", "S": "57"}}, "news": [{"title": "Odisha: 244 acres to be acquired for Jeypore Airport upgrade", "para": "The Odisha government is upgrading Jeypore Airport to Category 3C, requiring the acquisition of 244 acres. This expansion will allow the airport to handle 72-seater aircraft and operate 24/7, significantly boosting regional connectivity, economic growth, and tourism in southern Odisha.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/jeypore-airport-upgrade-244-acres-acquired-for-economic-growth-in-odisha/130488005?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-67568/130488005.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Margao, Mormugao ODPs to be converted into masterplans", "para": "Goa's Town and Country Planning Department is set to transform existing development plans for Margao and Mormugao into advanced GIS-based masterplans. This initiative, part of the Centre's Amrut 2.0 program, will create digital blueprints for these cities. The process involves detailed data collection on various urban aspects. Experts anticipate the conversion will take over a year to complete.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/transforming-margao-and-mormugao-new-gis-based-masterplans-under-amrut-20/130487971?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-23260/130487971.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Belagavi civic body's crackdown on illegal constructions raises accountability questions", "para": "Belagavi City Corporation intensified its drive against illegal constructions with a partial demolition of a four-storey building in Maruti Galli. The operation, while welcomed by some, has sparked controversy over alleged lack of notice and financial losses for tenants. Questions are also being raised about the corporation's monitoring and approval processes for such structures.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/belagavi-city-corporation-launches-major-offensive-against-illegal-constructions/130487930?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-62254/130487930.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}